{"tid":2323972,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"虛擬銀行WeLab Bank行政總裁辭任","createTime":"2020-12-13T14:53:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-13T16:00:27.000Z","uid":66271,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4e9d6617b2efee267a29aee3bc096184726380ca","tid":2323972,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T14:53:53.000Z","msg":"據報，虛擬銀行WeLab Bank證實，行政總裁謝學海已辭任，暫時由李家達接替。<br />\n<br />\n謝學海於2020年1月1日起出任行政總裁。他於銀行和金融業擁有近30年的經驗，在加入WeLab Bank之前，曾擔任台灣渣打銀行的首席財務官(CFO)和執行董事、保誠基金管理公司越南地區的首席執行官(CEO)，以及渣打零售銀行部地區財務主管與香港地區首席財務官。"},{"pid":"08d5875d27162e014c04cc711a2a8cad59baa239","tid":2323972,"uid":161374,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T14:54:52.000Z","msg":"無人用？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70f196e2e7a7afe9b154ec53a7f28df14b4099a5","tid":2323972,"uid":71526,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T14:57:13.000Z","msg":"個名聽都未撚聽過"},{"pid":"01368cb844b100f21088f4a58c8d7eed1aca7bdc","tid":2323972,"uid":183058,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T14:58:58.000Z","msg":"Lab 好似好化學咁，邊有人敢擺錢入去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c65c993ebac88a0e84db35a3b0932d0da6d0d91e","tid":2323972,"uid":249242,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T15:08:28.000Z","msg":"Virtual bank 個business model 同燒錢冇分別"},{"pid":"416d2c62098632dff9cdb8c7b67f7b1b4146767b","tid":2323972,"uid":134993,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"01368cb844b100f21088f4a58c8d7eed1aca7bdc","tid":2323972,"uid":183058,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T14:58:58.000Z","msg":"Lab 好似好化學咁，邊有人敢擺錢入去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T16:00:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}